title: Crunchy Chocolate Chip Mini Cookies - 10 Halloween Snack Packs
body_html:
Delight your trick-or-treaters with Partake's best-selling cookie flavor in a new, limited edition Halloween snack pack! Crunchy Chocolate Chip Mini Cookie Snack Packs bring the same big chocolate chip flavor you already know and love in a bite-sized form.

Safe for school and ideal for grab-and-go, these vegan, allergy-friendly & non-GMO mini chocolate chip cookies will go the distance to keep you satisfied.

Each box contains ten (10) individually-wrapped snack packs.

title: Harvest Variety Pack
body_html: LIMITED EDITION: Back by popular demand, one of our best-selling variety packs of all time is here—but with a twist and only for a short time. Stock up on Crunchy Ginger Snap Cookies, best-selling Soft Baked Pumpkin Spice Cookies, and our new, limited edition Pumpkin Spice Mix just in time for sweater weather.

title: Snack Pack - Pumpkin Spice (24 ct)
body_html:
Get a case of our seasonal, snack pack-sized fam favorite just in time for Pumpkin Spice season. These spiced, soft-baked cookies will warm any fall day. Like all things Partake, these cookies are gluten-free, vegan, allergy-friendly, and non-GMO.

Each snack pack is the ideal allergy-friendly, on-the-go addition to your everyday life. Cases include 24 individually-wrapped, 1.09 oz packages of Soft Baked Pumpkin Spice cookies (3 cookies per package).

title: GRIN Pumpkin Lovers Variety Pack
body_html:
LIMITED EDITION: Our Pumpkin Lover's Variety Pack has everything you need to celebrate pumpkin spice season like a champion—and like all things Partake, these cookies and muffin mix are vegan, non-GMO, gluten-free, and top 9 allergen-free.

Our Soft Baked Pumpkin Spice cookies have sold out the past 2 years for a reason! And our new Pumpkin Spice Muffin Mix is the perfect fit for anyone looking for fresh-baked pumpkin goodness. Both offerings are the ideal match for brunch or your afternoon tea or coffee.

title: GRIN Soft Baked Pumpkin Spice 5.5oz box
body_html: LIMITED EDITION: This fam favorite is back! There's a reason our Soft Baked Pumpkin Spice Cookies have sold out two years in a row! These spiced, soft-baked cookies will warm any fall day. Like all things Partake, these cookies are gluten-free, vegan, top 9 allergen-free, and non-GMO.

title: GRIN Pumpkin Spice Muffin Baking Mix 13oz box
body_html:
LIMITED EDITION: Hints of pumpkin, cinnamon, ginger, and nutmeg make our NEW Pumpkin Spice Muffin Mix a fall pantry must have. Make fresh-from-the-oven muffins in minutes—simply mix with a few simple ingredients, bake and enjoy.

Like all things Partake, our newest baking mix is made with better-for-you ingredients and is certified vegan, gluten-free, top 9 allergen-free and non-GMO.

title: GRIN Sesame Street Variety 4-Pack
body_html:
If warm, fresh from the oven cookies are what you crave, we're bringing you our best-selling Chocolate Chip & Birthday Cake flavors for a limited time!

We partnered with Sesame Street to create all new Cookie Baking Mixes that are easy to prepare and made to share—just add water and butter (or applesauce) to the mix.  These Limited Edition Cookie Baking Mixes are the ideal sometimes treat and feature our furry friends from Sesame Street, Elmo and Cookie Monster. Like all Partake products, our Cookie Baking Mixes are certified gluten-free, vegan, non-GMO, and top 9 allergen-free.

title: Soft Baked Variety Pack
body_html:
Enjoy your cookies on the softer side? Our Soft Baked Variety Pack is for you!


Available in your choice of 4-pack or 8-pack, now's a great time to stock up on all of our soft-baked cookie flavors: Chocolate Chip, Double Chocolate Brownie, Cookie Butter & our newest flavor—Lemon!

title: All the Cookies! Family Pack (8 Boxes)
body_html:
You can have everything! With our "All the Cookies!" Family Pack, enjoy all of our crave-worthy crunchy & soft-baked cookie flavors delivered to your door.


Includes one 5.5 oz box of each flavor. Crunchy: Chocolate Chip, Double Chocolate, Ginger Snap & Birthday Cake.
Soft Baked: Cookie Butter, Double Chocolate Brownie, Chocolate Chip, & Lemon.

title: GRIN Classic Pancake 10oz box
body_html:
Upgrade your everyday with our Classic Pancake & Waffle Mix. This gluten-free, plant-based, and allergy-friendly mix makes worry-free breakfasts in minutes! Just add water for fluffy pancakes. Whip up waffles with just water and oil. Like all Partake products, our Classic Pancake & Waffle Mix is certified vegan, non-GMO, gluten-free and top 9 allergen free.

Did you know? Our Pancake & Waffle Mix makes cakes, muffins, and more. See recipes.
